{
  "texts": [
    "The particle filter operates recursively as follows.",
    "The filtering density at time t can be written as p",
    "t-1 (x t-1 |y 0:t-1) admits the approximation",
    "which is sampled by first drawing an x j t-1 with probability w j t-1 then propagating according to a proposal density q (θ) t (x t |x t-1, y t) and finally, reweighting accordingly.",
    "This weighted resampling scheme is presented in Algorithm 1, recursive application of which corresponds to the particle filter."
  ]
}